---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 71
By: Cornelius Agrippa
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Separation-Sin=Anatomy of the Fallen State
  - Sacrifice-Death=Separation-Sin=Closing the Doors of the Senses
---
When (the faculty of the soul) is overwhelmed by too much commerce with the
flesh and occupied with the sensible soul of the body, (it) is not worthy to
command the divine substances.
